    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。标准UDP头部是8字节，也就是64位。那这64位里面怎么划分？Source Port和Destination Port各占多少位？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
