      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标准的划分：0到15位是Source Port，16到31位是Destination Port，然后32到47位是Length字段，48到63位是Checksum。最后64到95位留给业务数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
