    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出这个结构。标题定为\"Estructura del paquete UDP\"，用packet-beta格式展示这五个字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
