      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，把数据字段标注为\"Data (Retail_OrderManagement)\"。确认一下范围：0-15 Source Port，16-31 Destination Port，32-47 Length，48-63 Checksum，64-95 业务数据。对吗？",
